  68. module Int32 = struct

  70.   let of_int_exn =
  71.     match Sys.word_size with (* size of [int] *)

  74.     | 64 ->
  75.         fun n ->
  76.           if n < Int32.(to_int min_int) || n > Int32.(to_int max_int) then
  77.             Misc.fatal_errorf "Targetint.of_int_exn: 0x%x out of range" n
  78.           else
  79.             Int32.of_int n
  80.     | _ ->
  81.         assert false
  82.   let of_int32 x = x

  90. module Int64 = struct
